1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,329
People who have bulldog persistence, who can grab something and not let go, have an essential success quality.

2
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:16,450
Here are two suggestions for developing greater power to experiment, the ingredient that, when blended with persistence, gets results.

3
00:00:16,450 --> 00:00:17,890
1.

4
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:21,170
Tell yourself there is a way.

5
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,329
All thoughts are magnetic.

6
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:28,290
As soon as you tell yourself, I'm beaten, there's no way to conquer this problem,

7
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:33,569
negative thoughts are attracted, and each of these helps convince you that you are right,

8
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,010
that you are whipped.

9
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:44,210
Believe instead there is a way to solve this problem and positive thoughts rush into your mind to help you find a solution.

10
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:48,130
It's believing there is a way that is important.

11
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:59,890
Marriage counselors report no success in saving marriages until one and preferably both partners see that it is possible to win back happiness.

12
00:01:00,720 --> 00:01:09,329
Psychologists and social workers say an alcoholic is doomed to alcoholism until he believes he can beat his thirst.

13
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:13,730
This year, thousands of new businesses are being formed.

14
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:18,369
Five years from now, only a small portion will be still in operation.

15
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:25,089
Most of those who fail will say, competition was just too much, we had no choice but to quit.

16
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:30,369
The real problem is that when most people hit the tar, things are rough,

17
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:34,690
barrier, they think only defeat, and so they are defeated.

18
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:42,049
When you believe there is a way, you automatically convert negative energy, let's quit,

19
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:47,730
let's go back, into positive energy, let's keep going, let's move ahead.

20
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:55,010
A problem, a difficulty, becomes unsolvable only when you think it is unsolvable.

21
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:59,089
Attract solutions by believing solutions are possible.

22
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,369
Refuse.

23
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:05,730
Simply refuse to even let yourself say or think that it's impossible.

24
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,329
2.

25
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:10,130
Back off and start afresh.

26
00:02:10,559 --> 00:02:11,345
Often we stay so close to a problem for so long that we can't see new solutions or new approaches.
